author: Second Wind
description:
Studios desperately want it to be 2019 again (bringing back Downey and Evans for Secret Wars, Toy Story 5, the upcoming Frozen sequels), even if the sequels to 2019 movies are underperforming (Aquaman 2, The Marvels, Joker 2, Fury of the Gods!, Mufasa,  Downton Abbey 2, etc.)

title: Mufasa's Box Office Performance Proves Studios Can't Make it 2019 Again | The Backdrop
